{"id":296472,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/06/美国之音-台湾地震造成一人丧生/","date":"2013-06-02T14:46:40Z","modified":"2013-06-02T14:46:40Z","title":"美国之音 | 台湾地震造成一人丧生","content":"<p><div><small><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://fullrss.net/r/https/maps.google.com/maps?f=q&#038;source=embed&#038;hl=zh-CN&#038;geocode=&#038;q=%E5%8F%B0%E6%B9%BE+%E5%8D%97%E6%8A%95%E5%8E%BF%E4%BB%81%E7%88%B1%E4%B9%A1&#038;sll=23.725012,121.245117&#038;sspn=1.820407,2.469177&#038;g=%E5%8F%B0%E6%B9%BE%E5%8D%97%E6%8A%95%E5%8E%BF%E4%BB%81%E7%88%B1%E4%B9%A1&#038;ie=UTF8&#038;hq=&#038;hnear=%E5%8F%B0%E6%B9%BE%E5%8D%97%E6%8A%95%E5%8E%BF%E4%BB%81%E7%88%B1%E4%B9%A1&#038;ll=24.021374,121.125214&#038;spn=1.816245,2.469177&#038;t=m&#038;z=9\">查看大图</a></small></p>\n<p>台湾发生强烈地震，造成一人死亡，并引发一起天然气爆炸事件。<br /> <br />美国地质调查局将星期天这次地震强度定为6点2级，这次地震发生在当地下午1点43分，地点是台湾中部南投仁爱乡，震源深度为20公里。<br /> <br />台湾内政部消防署说，一名男子在阿里山登山过程中被落石击中身亡。<br /> <br />这次地震让全台湾都感到了震动，震感最明显的是台湾中部和南部，人们都跑到街道上避险。香港也有震感。<br /> <br />同一天稍早，菲律宾发生了震级为5点7级的地震，造成数十座建筑被毁，几个人受伤。</div>\n<div><img src=\"http://fullrss.net/v/b5751a1dab57f57671c5d503ab58280b/http/www.voachinese.com/content/taiwan-earthquakes/1673570.html\" /></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://fullrss.net/\">fullrss.net</a></div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<p><iframe src=\"https://docs.google.com/a/chinadigitaltimes.net/spreadsheet/embeddedform?hl=zh-CN&#038;formkey=dFc0V1d0REQ4RkJ5d25uWFowVTNhWUE6MQ\" width=\"510\" height=\"328\" frameborder=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\">Loading&#8230;</iframe></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=b4fd4ae247\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/mstlf\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代 </a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" val